nodes.text: This female Dathomirian was the mother of Dathomiri Witch Kaminne and Olianne Sihn of the Raining Leaves Clan on the planet Dathomir. Sihn's mother was the only female in their family line who did not have a problem rearing a child.
In 33 ABY, an uprising of the clan's male slaves occurred which resulted in the deaths of over two-thirds of the clan's population. Sihn's mother was among those who perished.
